This paper deals with radio resource management and power control techniques in cellular networks, specifically in the context of device-to-device (D2D) communication in LTE Advanced. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). Additionally, the paper involves optimization algorithms and performance evaluation, which could fall under cs.IT (Information Theory) and cs.SY (Systems and Control). The paper also discusses interference management, which could be relevant to cs.MM (Multimedia) and cs.CR (Cryptography and Security).
